  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Immobilization in the Postoperative Analgesia of Surgically Treated Distal Radius Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Immobilization in the Postoperative Analgesia of Patients With Distal Radius Fracture Treated With Volar Locking Plating: a Prospective, Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
